      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a screenplay for a new drama series. it's a multi-generational story about a Black family living in a suburban area. i want to write a really immersive scene of a typical Sunday dinner at their house to help set the tone for the viewers. can u give me some descriptive details on what that dinner might look and sound like? i want it to feel very authentic and lived-in.",
