    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start with the atmosphere, but it feels a bit generic, like it could be any family. I really want to lean into the specific cultural heritage of the family to make the scene pop and feel more \"authentic\" to a Black suburban household. Can you add more specific details about the food being served and the way the family interacts? Like, maybe some more traditional dishes and the specific kind of energy or \"vibe\" that's common in these types of gatherings?",
